    "description": "本課程介紹多元文化、職場與教育環境。授課語言為英語。講師將以英語授課，學生使用英語完成相關作業與進行課間討論。<br>This course is designed to introduce cultural diversity as well as the working and studying environment. English is used during the course, in teaching, assignments, and in class discussions.",
