    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1. 什麼是文化<br>2. 文化的特點<br>3. 文化認同與個人認同<br>4. 語言如何影響人們的想法<br>5. 食<br>6. 衣<br>7. 音樂<br>8. 舞蹈<br>9. 藝術 <br>10. 節慶與假日 <br>11. 運動<br>12. 環境<br>13. 宗教<br>14. 文化差異<br><br>",
        "en": "1. What is Culture?<br>2. Features of Culture <br>3. Cultural Identity VS Personal Identity<br>4. How does language influence how one thinks? <br>5. Food<br>6. Clothing<br>7. Music <br>8. Dance<br>9. Art <br>10. Celebrations and Holidays <br>11. Sports<br>12. The Environment<br>13. Religion<br>14. Talking about Differences<br>"
